 rgba(0,0,0,.5));margin-bottom:20px}.follow-name{font-size:56px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;margin-bottom:10px}.follow-title{font-size:30px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);margin-bottom:32px}.follow-btn{display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fb923c,#f97316);color:#fff;font-size:44px;font-weight:700;padding:22px 64px;border-radius:50px}.follow-actions{margin-top:26px;font-size:28px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55)}</style></head><body><div class=\"comp\"><div class=\"watermark-wrap\" id=\"watermark\"><img src=\"https://sns-hub-five.vercel.app/dr-iwatatsu.png\" alt=\"Dr.いわたつ\"><div class=\"watermark-name\">Dr.いわたつ</div></div><div class=\"scene\" id=\"s1\"><div class=\"hook-badge\" id=\"badge\">🧖‍♂️ 実験系</div><div class=\"hook-main\" id=\"hook\"><span class=\"hook-accent\">CGM</span>つけて<br>サウナに入ったら<br>血糖値が<span class=\"hook-accent\">激変</span>した</div><div class=\"hook-sub\" id=\"sub\">専門医がリアルデータで検証<br>予想外の結果が出た</div></div><div class=\"scene\" id=\"s2\"><div class=\"data-section\"><div class=\"data-title\">Before / After　CGMデータ</div><div class=\"data-split\"><div class=\"data-box before\"><div class=\"data-label before\">入浴中</div><div class=\"data-phase\">安静時 92 → 入浴10分</div><div class=\"data-value up\">+16↑</div><div class=\"data-note\">mg/dL 上昇</div></div><div class=\"data-arrow\">→</div><div class=\"data-box after\"><div class=\"data-label after\">セッション後</div><div class=\"data-phase\">3セット完了30分後</div><div class=\"data-value down\">-8↓</div><div class=\"data-note\">mg/dL 低下</div></div></div><div class=\"data-insight\">「サウナで血糖が下がる」は半分正解・半分不正解。<br>入浴中はむしろ上がっていた。</div></div></div><div class=\"scene\" id=\"s3\"><div class=\"mech-box\"><div class=\"mech-title\">なぜ入浴中に血糖が上がるのか</div><div class=\"mech-flow\"><div class=\"mech-step\"><div class=\"mech-icon\">🔥</div><div class=\"mech-text\">熱ストレスで交感神経が活性化</div></div><div class=\"mech-down\">↓</div><div class=\"mech-step\"><div class=\"mech-icon\">⚡</div><div class=\"mech-text\">アドレナリン・ノルアドレナリン分泌</div></div><div class=\"mech-down\">↓</div><div class=\"mech-step\"><div class=\"mech-icon\">🫀</div><div class=\"mech-text\">肝臓からグルコース放出（糖新生）</div></div><div class=\"mech-down\">↓</div><div class=\"mech-step\"><div class=\"mech-icon\">📈</div><div class=\"mech-text\">CGM値が一時的に上昇する</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"scene\" id=\"s4\"><div class=\"evidence-box\"><div class=\"evi-title\">習慣化するとどうなる？　研究データ</div><div class=\"evi-stat\">週4回以上</div><div class=\"evi-desc\">サウナを週4回以上習慣的に利用する人は、週1回以下の人に比べて<br><span style=\"color:#22d3ee;font-weight:900\">2型糖尿病リスクが有意に低下</span><br>（JAMA Intern Med 2018）</div><div class=\"evi-source\">📚 Laukkanen T, et al. JAMA Intern Med. 2018</div><div class=\"evi-note\">⚠ 糖尿病の方・インスリン使用中の方は<br>必ず主治医に相談してから</div></div></div><div class=\"scene\" id=\"s5\"><div class=\"follow-section\"><img class=\"follow-avatar\" src=\"https://sns-hub-five.vercel.app/dr-iwatatsu.png\" alt=\"Dr.いわたつ\"><div class=\"follow-name\">Dr.いわたつ</div><div class=\"follow-title\">糖尿病専門医・指導医 / 内分泌専門医 / 医学博士</div><div class=\"follow-btn\">フォローする</div><div class=\"follow-actions\">💾 保存 &nbsp; 📤 シェア</div></div></div></div><script>const tl=gsap.timeline({repeat:-1});tl.to('#s1',{opacity:1,duration:0.48},0.0).to('#badge',{opacity:1,duration:0.6},0.5).to('#hook',{opacity:1,scale:1,duration:1.08,ease:'back.out(1.7)'},1.0).to('#hook',{scale:1.04,duration:0.42,ease:'power1.inOut'},1.9).to('#hook',{scale:1,duration:0.3},2.5).to('#sub',{opacity:1,duration:0.72},2.2).to('#s1',{opacity:0,duration:0.48},6.4).to('#s2',{opacity:1,duration:0.48},7.2).from('.data-box',{opacity:0,y:40,duration:0.84,stagger:0.65,ease:'power2.out'},8.0).from('.data-arrow',{opacity:0,duration:0.48},9.3).from('.data-insight',{opacity:0,y:20,duration:0.72},10.4).to('#s2',{opacity:0,duration:0.48},14.4).to('#s3',{opacity:1,duration:0.48},15.2).from('.mech-step',{opacity:0,x:-40,duration:0.6,stagger:0.65,ease:'power2.out'},15.7).from('.mech-down',{opacity:0,duration:0.36,stagger:0.65},16.2).to('#s3',{opacity:0,duration:0.48},20.8).to('#s4